      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. SOKAI was prominent throughout when winning two back then got further back last time but came home hard into third and beaten 4.5 lengths at this track (22.81). Has a very good strike-rate from this draw, with three wins from four starts. Sure to be about the mark. 4. CONQUEROR stalked the lead from the inside draw before finishing third last start (30.13) at Sandown in Restricted WIN H over 515m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Overdue and is among the main hopes. 5. PHANTOM CARAT comes off an average effort last start when fifth at Murray Bridge Straight over 300m behind Low Block (17.43) in a Grade 6. Has ability and is one of the better chances. 7. ZING MATILDA is building a nice sequence of placings – hard to fault that form.\",\"runners\":[1,4,5,7],\"exclusive\":false}",
